name: ChromaChord F Maj 7 Pad
description:
Meditative ChromaChords: Series of audio chords paired with color impressionist images. Image should fluctuate as you shift and move during viewing. 
Series will include for each chord - Pad: Soft, Pad Alpha: Soft floating image, Pixel: Pixelated, and Pixelated Alpha: Pixelated floating image
Alpha versions are best viewed/displayed in a 3D gallery or the metaverse.
